Package lawnlayer

Class Info

  • java.lang.Object
    • lawnlayer.Info
  • public final class Info
extends java.lang.Object
    A constants-only class containing the information which are used across multiple classes in the 'lawnlayer' package. As its sole purpose is an information container, the class along with its attributes have been marked final to prevent inheritence and modifications.
